think there's much left for me to teach you...?

This cave has a lot of Porori! coming after you, so if you
want to protect the purity of a maiden, be careful. \!... I
wonder if there's anyone like that.

...Well, I'll give it to you just in case. There might be a
case where one in a thousand wants it...
